<p class="indent2" style="-uslm-lc:I13" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">For purposes of subparagraph (A), any policy issued after <date date="1983-12-31">December 31, 1983</date>, in exchange for a substantially similar policy issued on or before such date shall be treated as issued before <date date="1984-01-01">January 1, 1984</date>. A similar rule shall apply in the case of a series of exchanges.</p>
